CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 6, 1971, pg. 33, reads: "Mt. Carmel's Guest - Special guest for the St. Valentine's Day Frappe Sip and Fashion Show, sponsored by the Improvement Fund Committee of Mt. Carmel Baptist Church, North Side, will be Patrice King, 'Miss Teenage Pittsburgh.' The Affair will take place at Faith Presbyterian Church, 1601 Brighton Rod. at 4 P. M. Feb. 14."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing striped tie, and Patrice King Brown wearing long hair, knotted pearl or bead necklace, and large corsage, standing behind table with large floral arrangement
